---
const year = new Date().getFullYear();
---

<footer class="bg-vert-recre text-cream-gouter pt-16 pb-8 px-6 mt-20">
  <div class="container-narrow">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-[2fr_1fr_1fr_1fr] gap-12">
      <div>
        <div class="font-bagel text-3xl tracking-wide mb-3">CLUB RÉCRÉ</div>
        <p class="font-fraunces italic text-lg opacity-90 max-w-[320px] mb-4">
          Le magazine lifestyle des parents qui ont grandi dans les années 90 et veulent transmettre une enfance libre.
        </p>
        <p class="text-sm opacity-75 max-w-[320px] leading-relaxed">
          Site édité par <a href="https://talyco.io" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="font-semibold underline decoration-jaune-cassette underline-offset-2 hover:text-orange-sirop transition-colors">Talyco — agence marketing</a>.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h4 class="text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.25em] text-jaune-cassette font-bold mb-4">Lire</h4>
        <ul class="list-none space-y-2 text-sm opacity-85">
          <li><a href="/journal" class="hover:text-orange-sirop hover:opacity-100 transition-colors">Journal</a></li>
          <li><a href="/activites" class="hover:text-orange-sirop hover:opacity-100 transition-colors">Activités</a></li>
          <li><a href="/lifestyle" class="hover:text-orange-sirop hover:opacity-100 transition-colors">Lifestyle</a></li>
          <li><a href="/education" class="hover:text-orange-sirop hover:opacity-100 transition-colors">Éducation</a></li>
          <li><a href="/vintage" class="hover:text-orange-sirop hover:opacity-100 transition-colors">Mode vintage</a></li>
          <li><a href="/selections" class="hover:text-orange-sirop hover:opacity-100 transition-colors">Sélections</a></li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h4 class="text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.25em] text-jaune-cassette font-bold mb-4">Le Club</h4>
        <ul class="list-none space-y-2 text-sm opacity-85">
          <li><a href="/le-club" class="hover:text-orange-sirop hover:opacity-100 transition-colors">Manifeste</a></li>
          <li><a href="/newsletter" class="hover:text-orange-sirop hover:opacity-100 transition-colors">Newsletter</a></li>
          <li><a href="/marques" class="hover:text-orange-sirop hover:opacity-100 transition-colors">Marques vintage</a></li>
          <li><a href="/rss.xml" class="hover:text-orange-sirop hover:opacity-100 transition-colors">RSS</a></li>
          <li><a href="/contact" class="hover:text-orange-sirop hover:opacity-100 transition-colors">Contact</a></li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h4 class="text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.25em] text-jaune-cassette font-bold mb-4">Suivre</h4>
        <ul class="list-none space-y-2 text-sm opacity-85">
          <li><a href="https://www.instagram.com/clubrecre" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="hover:text-orange-sirop hover:opacity-100 transition-colors">Instagram</a></li>
          <li><a href="https://www.tiktok.com/@clubrecre" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="hover:text-orange-sirop hover:opacity-100 transition-colors">TikTok</a></li>
          <li><a href="https://www.pinterest.com/clubrecre" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="hover:text-orange-sirop hover:opacity-100 transition-colors">Pinterest</a></li>
          <li><a href="https://www.vinted.fr" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="hover:text-orange-sirop hover:opacity-100 transition-colors">Vinted</a></li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-12 pt-6 border-t border-cream-gouter/20 flex justify-between text-xs opacity-70 flex-wrap gap-3">
      <span>© {year} Club Récré · Édité par <a href="https://talyco.io" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="hover:text-orange-sirop">Talyco, agence marketing</a></span>
      <span><a href="/mentions-legales" class="hover:text-orange-sirop">Mentions légales</a> · <a href="/cgv" class="hover:text-orange-sirop">CGV</a> · <a href="/confidentialite" class="hover:text-orange-sirop">Confidentialité</a></span>
    </div>
  </div>
</footer>
